OL,3,CJewish man verbally attacked on tube
OL,4,Cprompting police probe
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after a young
OL,7,Fman was filmed staring aggressively
OL,8,Fand telling a Jewish man "your
OL,9,Freligion kills Muslims" on the London
OL,10,FUnderground.
OL,12,FBritish Transport Police have
OL,13,Fconfirmed officers have launched a
OL,14,Fprobe after a reports of antisemitism
OL,15,Fwere made.
OL,17,FThe video was shared online by the
OL,18,Fcharity the Campaign Against
OL,19,FAntisemitism and has been seen almost
OL,20,Ftwo million times on X.
