OL,6,FChief superintendent Chris Casey added
OL,7,Fin the thread: "When we investigate
OL,8,Fcrimes, we are required to search for
OL,9,Fall available evidence. That includes
OL,10,Fwitnesses.
OL,12,F"The video obviously is incredibly
OL,13,Fhelpful, but it would be remiss of us
OL,14,Fnot to also ask for witnesses. Someone
OL,15,Fmay have seen what happened before or
OL,16,Fafter, add more info."
